==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Roofless
<hw>Roof"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having no roof;
<as>as, a <ex>roofless</ex> house</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having no house or home; shelterless;
homeless.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rooflet</ent>⟦br⟧
